<p style="font-size: large">
    Specific to my project and critical issue of improving autonomous vehicle technology, I researched how a neuron within the brain of a dragonfly allows it to anticipate the movement trajectory of its prey. 
    These <b>STMD (Small Target Motion Detection) neurons</b> could have the potential to teach us how to create incredibly accurate motion prediction software that will give autonomous vehicles the next level of safety and improvement.
</p>

